"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"如果你看一个人不顺眼，那不是他的问题，而是你心中对他有太多的想法。 \\n 凡有所相皆为虚妄，若见诸相非相即见如来。——《金刚经》 \\n 当你把你的想法去掉，你再去看他，他没有变，但你的情绪就会消失了，这个时候你心中的状态没有了执念，也没有了妄念，就达到了如来的状态。 \\n It was the most painful, mind destroying, horrible moment I have ever experienced. But once I realized the problem was not you, but within me. I found Inner Peace, and was able to harness the flow of the universe.——master shifu 《Kung fu panda》 \\n 这曾是我之前从来没有体验过得最痛苦，最令人心碎，最可怕的时刻。但自从我发现问题并不在于你，而是在于我，我领悟到了内心平静，心如止水，从而能够利用宇宙之量。——乌龟师傅《功夫熊猫》 \\n inner peace ！ \\n 内心如果平静，外在便再无波澜。\",\"timestamp\":1634084931,\"title\":\"凡有所相皆为虚妄，若见诸相非相即见如来。\"},\"digest\":\"kUB_2bVxYeZ9X0cQk2iFGQkQ0a0cIQ37wKdy-FqoXQ8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x052F05287121c5F1cF5152FA835EbFaC65e723A0\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DcPQ-NcGgqKFxQfiLlfDoVaMTJ2bjotlbMAO5R0uNpQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3ioNFl3fzWJ7DpUDfrssvrBnQlm6aQMgWR-FewRuiQI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"vmFeQPFtrAsHA7jE4D-6QPUWlcdNc_MR1xRsknnrOwcxui2pEWQMXSsL-kfsGDaGBkycWk9inSc0u97wrsxBuQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x55b03d970a268f5cbbc86872aa7ea6c66ced5328f253777c449b204725f52d95570da3113f05f16bac356e99dcdfc32fc176060b7f81e85f58b64c4c8787ac5e1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DcPQ-NcGgqKFxQfiLlfDoVaMTJ2bjotlbMAO5R0uNpQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3ioNFl3fzWJ7DpUDfrssvrBnQlm6aQMgWR-FewRuiQI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"kUB_2bVxYeZ9X0cQk2iFGQkQ0a0cIQ37wKdy-FqoXQ8\"}"